Vodacom Won’t Compensate Customers Over Network Failure, Business Day Says

-- B y   F r a n z   W i l d
-- 
2011-08-03T05:17:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-03/vodacom-won-t-compensate-customers-over-network-failure-business-day-says.html
Vodacom Group Ltd. (VOD)  won’t compensate
South African customers who lost money because of a network
failure in June, Johannesburg-based Business Day said, citing
the company’s response to the nation’s Consumer Commission,
which demanded Vodacom make the payments.  Click here for web link  To contact the reporter on this story:
